    <refnamediv>
        <refname>break</refname>
        <refpurpose>interruption d'une boucle  </refpurpose>
    </refnamediv>
    <refsection>
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            A l'intérieur d'une boucle <literal>for</literal> ou <literal>while</literal>, la commande <literal>break</literal> force la boucle à se terminer.
        </para>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>Exemples</title>
        <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
k=0;
while 1==1,
	  k=k+1;
	  if k > 100 then
	     break
	  end;
end
 ]]></programlisting>
    </refsection>
